{"tid":1641813,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聯合國面臨資金短缺危機，將可能冇糧出","createTime":"2019-10-09T12:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T16:19:20.000Z","uid":64191,"like":312,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":154,"replies":[{"pid":"fff040d9870f6234548fa930419733a8b579ff42","tid":1641813,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:55:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.un.org/en/story/2019/10/1048782\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2019%2F10%2F1048782&d=B%2BAVUFxUUUF%2FouYpVm7lNkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=8623803e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.un.org/en/story/2019/10/1048782</a><br />\n<br />\nThe United Nations is facing a severe shortage of cash, and unless more Governments pay their annual dues, &ldquo;our work and our reforms are at risk&rdquo;, the UN chief Ant&oacute;nio Guterres told Member States on Tuesday.<br />\n<br />\n聯合國主席Antonio Guterres星期二向成員國表示，聯合國正面臨嚴重既現金短缺，除非更多成員國準時交年費，否則工作及改革都會有風險<br />\n<br />\n聯合國秘書處已經去信至成員國，指聯合國既資金危機係接近十年來最嚴重既一次，現正冒著月底前會耗盡流動儲備、拖欠工作人員薪酬及向供應商付款既風險<br />\n<br />\n雖然193成員國已有129個找數，但聯合國發言人繼續催未找數既交錢，咁樣先可以避免在全球既營運受到破壞<br />\n<br />\n到9月為止，全年估算額得70%係找左數，比舊年同期少8%。到10月8日為止，成員國已經為2019年常規預算畀左19.9億美元，仍然有13億美元款項未收到<br />\n<br />\n現金短缺到10月，將會達到6億美元，意味著聯合國將會冇足夠既錢，去畀9月既大會辯論及最高級別會議既費用。聯合國再重申，唔找足數，秘書處11月會冇糧出、貨物及服務都冇錢畀。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國秘書長Guterres響預算制定第五委員會中，指出今個月聯合國將面臨十年來最嚴重既赤字，<br />\n<br />\n通過2020預算計劃後，支出將與2019年維持不變，總額為29.4億美元，包括裁減接近100個職位。秘書長Guterres指呢個方案係「對我地前進既深刻反映，以及共同作業既堅定承諾」<br />\n<br />\n「然而組織正面臨流動性危機，冇錢就實現唔到目標喇」上星期，秘書長警告，由於已經動用緊急措施，將令到職位空缺無法填補、會議要取消、旅遊僅限基本級別。紐約、日內瓦、維也納及內羅畢，以及區域委員會既工作都會大幅影響<br />\n<br />\n簡單講句，就係叫成員國課金呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a931f210fc0adde797c0006806482ac17b1935c5","tid":1641813,"uid":64191,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:55:52.000Z","msg":"原文係長篇英文，內容多重覆，我盡量搵重點翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然有殘體中文版本"},{"pid":"28a9ede5488c845cc0915e2e27ea1b6c1506756b","tid":1641813,"uid":550,"like":71,"dislike":1,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:56:40.000Z","msg":"俾台灣入去咪有錢收囉"},{"pid":"9b5da0fb3736e75d7e64e0ad8c0758f5c620569c","tid":1641813,"uid":34777,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:57:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>終國有冇錢交？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3eacb413af4bab3ede25b3c30836458a73b619d5","tid":1641813,"uid":274149,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:58:57.000Z","msg":"抵死。咁新共，叫中共同他的阿非拉兄弟比"},{"pid":"35b02090a88cf229b80de3ccaa615958dab9ec84","tid":1641813,"uid":251945,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:00:16.000Z","msg":"無人想課金比垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e169a84aad5d2cb58aa10e1d7a2a0b0938a02d","tid":1641813,"uid":88823,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:03:04.000Z","msg":"叫中國課啦 人地咁撚有錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444358252ec17ed71d536a91c6d1d15f0cf39fdb","tid":1641813,"uid":289978,"like":84,"dislike":1,"score":83,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:04:20.000Z","msg":"垃圾聯合國，執撚左佢啦。"},{"pid":"78c94cb8f6467c8e9847303fb8bc344c78bff6dc","tid":1641813,"uid":263221,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:08:51.000Z","msg":"中國堂堂大國仲唔做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757b7bcce9a68e774b27f8b08703208758fed7a2","tid":1641813,"uid":143230,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T13:13:25.000Z","msg":"係時候執柒左去玩ww3"},{"pid":"1cf79bead6f8e5d9de7da0f4b9bcafe505165782","tid":1641813,"uid":49197,"